{
  "2146720": {
    "name": "深空幸存者",
    "steam_appid": 2146720,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146720/extras/45f230c788d019e61301b9a7bd524edf.avif?t=1758817497\" width=608 height=168 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将驾驶着战机冲向宇宙，在无穷无尽的敌人包围中作战并收集资源。完成任务并击毁敌方boss，成为这片宇宙最后的幸存者！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146720/extras/73eeea479768c4cf50b2eda23c1035fa.webp?t=1758817497\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这片宇宙中，你的生还对人类至关重要，你将同时面对动辄上百的敌方战机，你唯一能信赖的只有自己，敌人源源不断，无穷无尽！但无需畏惧，尽情的叩动发射键，击毁他们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146720/extras/c3ff6c625d37d73cdcf9bb67c21799ff.poster.avif?t=1758817497\" width=610 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146720/extras/c3ff6c625d37d73cdcf9bb67c21799ff.webm?t=1758817497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146720/extras/c3ff6c625d37d73cdcf9bb67c21799ff.mp4?t=1758817497\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗节奏紧张且刺激，敌人的进攻来势凶猛。你需要在战斗中尽快收集经验，强化自己的战机。要记住！时刻打起精神！迎接随时发生的战斗！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146720/extras/556cddd991da505c6e70617e4bd5de93.poster.avif?t=1758817497\" width=610 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146720/extras/556cddd991da505c6e70617e4bd5de93.webm?t=1758817497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146720/extras/556cddd991da505c6e70617e4bd5de93.mp4?t=1758817497\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请时刻铭记你的任务，收集资源才是关键。你需要在狭小的区域内停留并收集资源，当然，敌人的进攻不会停歇，考验你技术的时刻到了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146720/extras/ad94c4b0a6c9b2a8d65c33ae92bde02f.poster.avif?t=1758817497\" width=610 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146720/extras/ad94c4b0a6c9b2a8d65c33ae92bde02f.webm?t=1758817497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146720/extras/ad94c4b0a6c9b2a8d65c33ae92bde02f.mp4?t=1758817497\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >前往宇宙尽头挑战敌方boss。在漫天弹幕中遨游穿梭，彻底摧毁这些敌人，你便是当之无愧的幸存者！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146720/extras/7a94f7ed1e1188c4da90b82f89b3fe75.poster.avif?t=1758817497\" width=610 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146720/extras/7a94f7ed1e1188c4da90b82f89b3fe75.webm?t=1758817497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146720/extras/7a94f7ed1e1188c4da90b82f89b3fe75.mp4?t=1758817497\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146720/extras/11aeacade3151ceb7a77dbdf76e35c10.webp?t=1758817497\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >八艘属性各不相同的战机</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >十二种独特的战机升级系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >数十款武器和特殊装备</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这无穷无尽的组合中，你将会创造出独属于自己的战机，去迎接更多的挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146720/extras/471ff24dab163c46a4b30e6710ed4f2a.poster.avif?t=1758817497\" width=610 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146720/extras/471ff24dab163c46a4b30e6710ed4f2a.webm?t=1758817497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146720/extras/471ff24dab163c46a4b30e6710ed4f2a.mp4?t=1758817497\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >近百种武器搭配，在每一次游戏中，都会有不同的体验</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146720/extras/19fd1379dcd5b9fa8f3e3b79026fc128.avif?t=1758817497\" width=598 height=464 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146720/extras/4028bf34b3bd37e3eacc2f3d7881f634.webp?t=1758817497\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在多种游戏模式下探索27个地图：生存，逃脱和歼灭。遭遇数十种敌人风格，随机升级路径，以及每个任务中的新挑战。释放你内心的太空战士，加入【深空幸存者】的行动！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146720/extras/29793f2c8149e717315375f251af9176.poster.avif?t=1758817497\" width=610 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146720/extras/29793f2c8149e717315375f251af9176.webm?t=1758817497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146720/extras/29793f2c8149e717315375f251af9176.mp4?t=1758817497\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
